Introduction

LE’V, also known as Wang Zi Hao, is a Chinese singer under Chromosome Entertainment. He made his solo debut on August 18, 2023, with the EP A.I.BAE.

He is best known for being a contestant on the reality survival show “Boys Planet” finishing in 19th place, not making the final lineup.
